'''Cam Kennedy''' is a Scottish comics artist. He was the illustrator of the ''[[Star Wars: Dark Empire]]'', ''[[Star Wars: Dark Empire II]]'' and most of the [[Star Wars: Boba Fett (comic series)|''Star Wars: Boba Fett'']] comics series. He also illustrated [[Empire 7|''Empire'' 7]] and the covers for [[Classic Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back 2|''Classic Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back'' 2]], ''[[Jabba the Hutt: The Gaar Suppoon Hit]]'' and [[Star Wars Tales 18|''Star Wars Tales'' 18]]. Kennedy was born and raised in Scotland and spent seven years painting in France before becoming a comic artist.<ref name="DEII TPB">[[Star Wars: Dark Empire II (TPB)|''Dark Empire II'' trade paperback]]</ref>

